import React, { useState } from "react"; import InputField from "./InputField"; import SelectField from "./SelectField"; import { educationOptions } from "../constants/form"; import Section from "./Section"; import { sendDetails } from "../api"; import { SchemaTypes, formatObject, formatValue, validateData } from "../utils"; const defaultForm = { email: "", fullName: "", age: "", education: "", institute: "", program: "", experience: "", canadaInstitute: "", canadaProgram: "", country: "", goals: "", scoresListening: "", scoresReading: "", scoresSpeaking: "", scoresWriting: "", isPaidTutionFees: null, paidTutionAmount: "", isGic: null, paidGicAmout: "", }; const schema = { email: SchemaTypes.string(true), fullName: SchemaTypes.string(true), age: SchemaTypes.number(true), education: SchemaTypes.string(true), institute: SchemaTypes.string(true), program: SchemaTypes.string(true), experience: SchemaTypes.string(true), canadaInstitute: SchemaTypes.string(true), canadaProgram: SchemaTypes.string(true), country: SchemaTypes.string(true), goals: SchemaTypes.string(true), scoresListening: SchemaTypes.number(true), scoresReading: SchemaTypes.number(true), scoresSpeaking: SchemaTypes.number(true), scoresWriting: SchemaTypes.number(true), isPaidTutionFees: SchemaTypes.boolean(true), paidTutionAmount: SchemaTypes.number(true), isGic: SchemaTypes.boolean(true), paidGicAmout: SchemaTypes.number(true), }; export default function Form() { const [form, setForm] = useState(defaultForm); const handleChange = (value, name) => { setForm((prevState) => ({ ...prevState, [name]: value })); }; const handleSubmit = (e) => { e.preventDefault(); const errors = validateData(schema, form); const formatted = formatObject(schema) console.log(errors, "errors"); console.log(formatted, "formatted"); // sendDetails(form); }; return (
